works.description:
Dartz, the Russian tuner that never fails  
to hit the news with its bespoke rides, has now teamed up with famous  
airbrush artist A.C’machoFF to create a unique Harley that perfectly fits  
our list of custom Harley-Davidsons cloaked in perfection. The Dartz  
Harley-Davidson is a unique mix of new Russian chic - gold and silver  
details with silver tzars coins and an airbrushed with Soviet symbols  
helmet.
